It is infinitely easier to form alliances based upon what we hate, rather than what we love.¬†

Take Antifa for instance. They are not all Communists, some are Anarchists, some are Feminists, some are pro-Palestine, some are pro-Israel, some are just paid protesters. However when the Left comes to power, the strongest faction will surely purge the weaker factions. The strongest faction will not be White Antifa punks, it will probably be Mexican Socialists.

We on the Right have had a lot of problems getting along because we are a "pro-values" movement. Because of this, we argue all day about our values rather than focusing our attention on destroying our enemies. Thus, we fall into years of counterproductive debates over "optics" or Paganism vs Christianity.

Conversely, during the election, we were all unified as being "anti-Hillary" and "anti-Globalist" thus, we were able to focus our efforts on defeating our enemies rather than infighting over minutae.

Gab has become a clusterfuck of infighting because we are all pretty much on the same page. There is no real enemy here so we just fight with one another over the 5% of issues we disagree on.

When these non-Whites get in power they will specifically attack White women. Women account for a major chunk of the Left's voter base. We need to capture this demographic using¬†emotional propaganda and bring them to our side, both for political reasons and to stop White genocide.

One of the consequences of a two party system is the political ebb and flow that happens as we go from Right to Left to Right to Left.

As 2020/2024 approaches and dissatisfaction with Trump/Republicans increases, we will need to hijack the Left's political momentum and steer it in a direction that gets White women to be anti-immigrant and anti-establishment.

We need to include in our platform promises of "Mother's Aide" to married White mothers (to encourage a return to Traditional gender roles, get women out of the workforce and increase White birth rates), "National Health Care" (basic major medical coverage for all citizens), mass deportations of all illegals, a complete denial of all services and entitlements to illegals and criminals as well as harsh penalties on perpetrators of migrant crimes (we'll use personalized examples of violence against women like we did with Kate Steinle).

If we do this, I think we stand a real chance of getting many of these women on our side.

Let's be honest, these women are largely apolitical but are coerced by peer pressure to be anti-Right Wing.

We need to incentivize women to come to our side and scare the crap out of them so they seek our protection.
